@49   = ~No, instead. My own figure is so great that it could blind anyone. Including the small people.~
@50   = ~Er... Modesty isn't your strong point...~
@51   = ~I couldn't help but notice, little one, that you never allow yourself any carnal pleasure. Are you one of those males that only act on female orders, then?~
